Number of Digits
Send Feedback
Given the number 'n', find out and return the number of digits present in a number .
Input Format :
Integer n
Output Format :
Count of digits
Constraints :
1 <= n <= 10^6
Sample Input 1 :
 156
Sample Output 1 :
3
Sample Input 2 :
 7
Sample Output 2 :
1

Solution :

public class Solution {

	public static int count(int n){
		//Write your code here
		int count =0;
		if(n ==0){
			return 0;
		}
		count = 1 + count(n/10);
		return count;
}
}
